videos.description: Virginia's Mamadi Diakite puts down the strong two-handed dunk off the great pass from Devon Hall.
videos.headline: Diakite throws down the hammer

videos.description: North Carolina's Joel Berry II puts in the highly contested layup for the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: Berry II makes the difficult basket

videos.description: Virginia's Jack Salt comes up with the strong block on North Carolina's Gerrison Brooks' layup attempt.
videos.headline: Salt denies Brooks

videos.description: Virginia's Devon Hall makes the great steal and takes it down court to throw down the monster dunk, as the Cavaliers lead over the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: Hall turns defense into offense

videos.description: Virginia head coach Tony Bennett praises his team's uptempo pace as it has the lead over the Tar Heels going into halftime.
videos.headline: Bennett: "We do our best"

videos.description: Virginia's De'Andre Hunter drives from the baseline to throw down the monster one-handed dunk, and Dick Vitale exclaims Hunter is "channeling his inner Jordan".
videos.headline: Hunter makes Vitale go 'wow'

videos.description: Virginia's Kyle Guy makes a great pass to connect with Isaiah Wilkins, who finishes with the strong two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Wilkins with the two-handed jam

videos.description: Dick Vitale and Bob Wischusen break down Virginia's dominant defense against North Carolina as the Cavaliers take down the Tar Heels 61-49.
videos.headline: Vitale: Virginia 'put on a clinic' against UNC
